GENERATING THE EGG
===================

$ python setup.py bdist_egg


TESTING THE EGG
================

>>> import sys
>>> sys.path.append('my_egg-0.1-py2.7.egg')
>>> from my_package.my_module import MyClass
>>> myClass = MyClass()
All gone to Hell!


